message.body: Keep meaning to email to say I had so much fun on my trip and am so proud if you and hit me up when you make that feature. Xo

Aww thanks boo! I had a blast. I am so glad you were there to experience it with me, my oldest and best friend. Thanks for spending the time and money. It will be up there in my most memorable experiences, next to the hfstival.
Haha nothing can top hfstival. Love ya.
